♪An ending that can never be undone♪

202
00:11:02,075 --> 00:11:05,795
♪Disrupting the old rhythm,
laying traps♪

203
00:11:06,050 --> 00:11:08,461
♪A board full of snares♪

204
00:11:08,462 --> 00:11:14,407
♪Carving the past
into every smile and word♪

205
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:18,970
♪After falling, still searching for♪

206
00:11:19,187 --> 00:11:21,661
♪The old marks♪

207
00:11:21,662 --> 00:11:25,924
♪Pages filled with attempts
to hide the past♪

208
00:11:25,925 --> 00:11:28,161
♪The next page♪

209
00:11:28,162 --> 00:11:31,370
♪Is turned, revealing this land
of right and wrong♪

